45:41.999 --> 45:45.124
But you have to give me
something I can bounce off of,

45:45.208 --> 45:47.667
-or else...
-Okay. Okay.

45:48.416 --> 45:50.958
Look, um...

45:56.792 --> 45:58.541
You know, in some churches,
they say,

45:58.625 --> 46:01.083
"You need to let go
in order to let God in,"

46:01.166 --> 46:04.500
and this is more like, uh...

46:05.333 --> 46:07.999
"You need to let go
in order to...

46:10.375 --> 46:11.375
let...

46:14.041 --> 46:15.667
something in."

